metadata.name: Floodjumper
metadata.description:
Floodjumper by dubHz0

A lone figure jumps to undercover shelter from a torrential downpour in a small township in rural South Africa.  
The backdrop of a brightly painted pink building covered with barbed security wire and security mesh over the window providing a strange context.  
Raindrops and reflections providing a natural filter and reality to the image.  
Narrative. Documentary. Photography.
